# data/
# Test images နှင့် videos ကို ဒီနေရာမှာ ထားပါ။
#
# Recommended structure:
#   data/
#   ├── images/       ← *.jpg, *.png test images
#   ├── videos/       ← *.mp4, *.avi test videos
#   └── gallery/      ← face registration images (1 person per subfolder)
#       ├── person_a/
#       └── person_b/
